content:
apiVersion: apps/v1
kind: Deployment
metadata:
  name: s3-demo
spec:
  replicas: 1
  selector:
    matchLabels:
      app: s3-demo
  template:
    metadata:
      labels:
        app: s3-demo
    spec:
      containers:
      - name: s3-demo-postgres
        image: postgres:latest
        env:
        - name: POSTGRES_DB
          value: 's3demo'
        - name: POSTGRES_PASSWORD
          value: 's3demo'
        - name: POSTGRES_USER
          value: 's3demo'
        - name: POSTGRES_HOST_AUTH_METHOD
          value: 'md5'
        ports:
        - containerPort: 5432
      - name: s3-demo-ua
        image: universal-agent:7.3.0.0
        env:
        - name: UAGNETNAME
          value: 's3-demo-ua'
        - name: UAGOMSSERVERS
          value: '8899@host.docker.internal'
        - name: UAGTRANSIENT
          value: 'yes'
        - name: UAGAGENTCLUSTERS
          value: 's3_processing'
        - name: UAGBUSINESSSERVICES
          value: 'Data_Ops'
